        public Club(java.util.UUID club_id,
            java.lang.String clubName,
            java.lang.String street,
            java.lang.String suburb,
            java.lang.String state,
            java.lang.String postcode,
            java.lang.String presidentName,
            java.lang.String presidentContact,
            double weeklyFee,
            double totalFee)
        USED ONLY WHEN THE DATA IS LOADED FROM THE DATABASE
        Parameters:
        club_id - ID number from database
        clubName - Name of the Club
        street - The street address, also includes street number
        suburb - The suburb the club is located in
        state - The state the club is in
        postcode - The postcode (zip code) for the suburb
        presidentName - The name of the president/chairman of the club
        presidentContact - Contact info for the president/chairman, can be phone or email
        totalFee - The total fee over the year to be paid by the club for admin and match officials
        weeklyFee - The total current weeks fee to be paid by the club for match officials and admin
        Since:
        1.0
